                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Dataset Selection Strategy</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
                        Choosing the right dataset is critical for realistic NIDS. We start with <strong>NSL-KDD</strong> for rapid prototyping due to its smaller size, then scale to <strong>UNSW-NB15</strong> or <strong>CICIDS2017</strong> for modern enterprise traffic realism.
                    </p>
                    
                    <!-- Chart Container 1 -->
